parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle weld can cause loss of control, noise, and vibration, leading to accidents or difficulty driving.

sudden shifting into reverse or other gears

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slippage can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or difficulty driving.

clunking noise when braking in reverse
